title: AI Tokens Jump on Irrational Euphoria as Musk’s X Corp Reveals xAI Shareholding
description: Developments in key AI companies sometimes drive gains in AI-focused tokens as traders bet on the long-term growth of such tokens.

title: Singapore’s Digital Money Revolution: Wholesale CBDC Takes Center Stage
description: The Monetary Authority of Singapore has unveiled a digital money strategy focusing on wholesale CBDC, tokenized bank liabilities, and regulated stablecoins, excluding retail CBDC. Local banks OCBC and UOB are testing interbank settlements using digital tokens, and MAS plans to extend this to cross-border transactions.
